   Television Producer,
   9 Partners to Buy
   San Diego Padres
   ---
   Tom Werner's Group Agrees
   To Pay Heiress Joan Kroc
   $75 Million for the Team
   ----
   By Richard Turner
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
